              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36443377/" class="">文化大革命</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52112538/" class=" " title="puma">puma</a>
                (读史早知今日事。)
              
